Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we're going to speak on what is meant by spiritual.\NOh my, that's a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.03,0:00:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.\NReligious is easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.25,0:00:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Religion is easy, but what is meant by spiritual?\NSpiritual is the essence of religion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NSpiritual means the realization that one's reality is beyond the physical,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.24,0:00:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,that it involves other realms.\NThese other realms have different qualities, non-physicality, non-locality.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,To feel the presence of God is so overwhelming, but there's no way of explaining it.\NIf a person has ever had the experience of the presence of divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:01:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very hard to explain to them.\NBut you can attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a great feeling of beatitude and beauty,\Nand you're aware that there is an infinite presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite presence becomes overwhelming and dominates all that exists.\NAnd then as one's talking, one realizes that that same spirit is what is speaking through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What is speaking through me right now is of divine origin,\Nthe spiritual energy of the ultimate reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think I'm starting to understand this,\Nand one way that you can promote our knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is by getting the attention of the divine spirit into the inner world.\NThat's—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NIt's really about the inner world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and the inner world is a struggle.\NSo, I would say that it's really a struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a challenge because it's an inner world.\NIt's a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.71,0:02:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But, as Dr. David said,\Nit's not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a challenge.\NIt's a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.65,0:02:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot stop your desire\Nand you cannot stop living your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.56,0:02:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain level and incomprehensible to people who calibrate below that level.\NThere are people who are so anti-spiritual that they are not permeable to spiritual reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's other ways of communicating with such individuals, but it's not through direct\Nawareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.80,0:02:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it via a judge and a cop.\NKilling your neighbors is wrong and we will put you into jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we come into this lifetime of incarnate, do we choose the lessons that we have to learn\Nin this lifetime?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we choose but not in the customary meaning of the term choose, like a this versus a that.\NIt's more like a climate, like we choose a certain climate, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I choose a wife who is spiritually oriented and capable of comprehending and responding\Nto spiritual reality without being specific, you know, you didn't have to grow up in a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,certain religion or live in a certain place, but we share certain overall major values.\NSo we may differ about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NWe may differ about individual clouds, but not about the nature of the sky itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:04:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NI just wondered because the climate, you know, it's like choosing the climate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think that's exactly correct.\NSo we've established a climate for our own lives in which spiritual realities have the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,top priority.\NAnd they are interactive with our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They are interactive with our daily actions and behaviors and beliefs and thoughts and\Nspeech to varying degrees depending on the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, right now we're speaking about it directly because it's appropriate to speak\Nso directly, but on the way back home again, we will not speak about it so specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so directly, but it will still be a dominant presence, even though we're not on the subject,\Nso we may be talking about the dominant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NWe may be talking about the dog or the temperature of the thermostat, but it's in an overall
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,setting which is predominantly spiritual and devoted to infinite peace and the presence\Nof God as an unspoken awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's one that half America does.\NWhat?
