Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, each of us has our own propensities coming from childhood training and I think\Nthe dominance of certain sensory modalities over other people, the sense of taste is quite
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,acute and important in their life and the other people is like an appreciative but dutiful\Nhusband.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NAnd I mean like, yeah, I serve whatever is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NI serve whatever is served for lunch, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:06:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be French toast, it could be bacon, it could be a peanut butter sandwich.\NAnd a lot of times when you say to me, you know, what do you want me to make, I'll say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.18,0:06:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,a peanut butter sandwich is fine.\NIn other words, I don't want you to go to any trouble, a specific trouble, because I
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,get sufficient pleasure out of anything you make and a peanut butter sandwich to me is\Nfantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people would say, oh, a peanut butter sandwich, you know what I mean?\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they want Swiss steak every day, I guess.\NSo that, all right, now spirit, as far as it goes, the spiritual student could still
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,be spiritual without concentrating on their weight loss.\NOh, they wouldn't have anything to do with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can contextualize the weight problem within spiritual parameters or not.\NIf you want to make it a spiritual problem, well then, it becomes a spiritual problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a spiritual problem.\NIt becomes a spiritual problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It becomes a spiritual problem.\NI guess so.
